    public static final class PartnerAccount.Partner.Builder
extends com.google.protobuf.GeneratedMessageV3.Builder<PartnerAccount.Partner.Builder>
implements PartnerAccount.PartnerOrBuilder
     Specifies information about a partner organization that has an account opened with Bloombox. A partner can own/manage
 multiple `Location`s, and is identified uniquely by a short `code`, which is a lowercase string suitable for use in
 a URL as a slug.
    Protobuf type bloombox.schema.partner.Partner
